ar. Physical and\ndynamical gas conditions are inferred by modelling the CO spectrum. Finally, we\nderive a direct measurement of the stellar mass of $M_*\\sim$14.7$^{+2}_{-3.6}$\nM$_{\\odot}$ by combining our interferometric and spectral modelling results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2020 16:51:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-25"}
