 supra-solar Al/Si and Mg/Si ratios of the Earth are\ndue to the accretion of ~40% of the mass of our planet from the\nfirst-generation of refractory-rich planetesimals.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Mar 2020 18:53:09 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-08"}
