. Experimental results confirm that RoboFuzz makes a success rate of up to\n93.3% in imposing concrete threats to the robot while the overall loss of work\nefficacy is merely 4.1% at the mitigation mode.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2020 01:30:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-14"}
