ynamics\nsimulations of active systems, and theories of glassy dynamics and 2D fluid\nfilms, we develop a dynamical state diagram that predicts the state of the\ncolony, and the mechanisms governing their 2D-to-3D transitions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2020 04:51:55 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-13"}
