 non-monotonicity of the c-functions\nfor several anisotropic configurations, which however does not contradict with\nany of the existing c-theorems since they all base on Lorentz invariance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2020 15:28:07 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 12 May 2020 12:39:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-26"}
