tate-of-the-art methods, ACGPN can generate\nphoto-realistic images with much better perceptual quality and richer\nfine-details.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Mar 2020 15:55:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-03-13"}
